Sentencas: Perovskite Ba0.8La0.2FeO3-delta was synthesized via a glycine-nitrate process as the cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Preparation and electrochemical properties of Ba0.8La0.2FeO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Ultra-fine pure phase Ba0.8La0.2FeO3-delta powder was obtained after the self-propagating combustion of a complex xerogel precursor.
Titulo: Preparation and electrochemical properties of Ba0.8La0.2FeO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The Ba0.8La0.2FeO3-delta cathode showed good compatibility and an enhanced phase interface with a samarium-doped ceria electrolyte.
Titulo: Preparation and electrochemical properties of Ba0.8La0.2FeO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical measurements showed that the Ba0.8La0.2FeO3-delta cathode achieved a low polarization resistance of 0.58 Omega cm(2) at 800 A degrees C in an air atmosphere.
Titulo: Preparation and electrochemical properties of Ba0.8La0.2FeO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The porous nanostructure guaranteed the catalytic activity for the oxygen reduction reaction, even if the cathode material possessed a cobalt-free and low rare earth composition.
Titulo: Preparation and electrochemical properties of Ba0.8La0.2FeO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
